then we can make use of [**`sum :: (Foldable f, Num a) =&gt; f a -&gt; a`**](https://hackage.haskell.org/package/base-4.12.0.0/docs/Prelude.html#v:sum) and [**`map :: (a -&gt; b) -&gt; [a] -&gt; [b]`**](https://hackage.haskell.org/package/base-4.12.0.0/docs/Prelude.html#v:map) to map a list of points to a list of *x*-coordinates:

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;xSum :: [Point] -&amp;gt; Double
